de.feu.showgo.ui.dialogs

Class RolesSelectDialog

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.feu.showgo.ui.dialogs.RolesSelectDialog

  • public class RolesSelectDialog
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains a dialog for selecting roles. A list of roles is displayed to the user. He can select roles using checkboxes and confirm or cancle his selection. It is used for assigning pseudo roles to a role.
